text: Yo ragahv! U r one of the most social and friendly person I have met in iitk. First year me NCC wale bhi kya hi din the, bc attendance ke liye kaise bhagte the hum. Fir techkriti me sath me junior and senior executive. I will always cherish those days. Sath me canteen jana and zomato swiggy se order dena was our routine during 2nd year summers. You are a natural dancer, an amazing guitar player and singer. Bhai apne kitne trips cancel hue hai yaad hai. Hum dono phone par plans discuss karte the and finally plans cancel ho jate the ğŸ˜‚ Lucknow and Goa me bhot maje aaye. I hope ki kabhi main bhi teri trah confidently flirt karna sikh jauğŸ˜›. Also, you were right and I regret going to the LPK. But koi baat nhi kuch nya pehli bar try kiya. Covid ke bad phir se koi trip plan karte hai. And thanks to you for introducing crypto trading to the wing. Stay in touch bro!
author: Arpit Kumar Jhunjhunwala

text:
Yo chandler bing of the wing, the bond of friendship we share is evident from the fact that almost every other group photo includes you. Tera sense of humour to alag level hai, aise hi sabko hasate and haste rho. bc jangid ka kitna kata hai tune first year me. Din bhar light band kar ke magta hai mobile par phir bolta kuch padha hi nhi. Alag level chapu hai tu. Har roj tere room par knock karna and puchna 'canteen chalega', roj subah ek dusre ko breakfast ke liye uthana, sath me swiggy zomato se order karna, I will miss all those days. Ashu ka room was our hangout spot. Jab bulla katna ho chalo chalo Ashu ke room me. U r the real ambani of the wing. Itna bada ghar hai ki room se kitchen tak bluetooth nhi pakadta. Apne jitne plans cancel hue hai un sab me bc tu sabse pehle kat ta tha but finally Goa me to alag hi level maje aaye. Tere sath pehli bar air travel karna and exploring the airports was another memorable experience. Mobile change karte hi pubg pro ban gya tu, valo me kab odin chalana band karega bc. Main bhi try karta hu Bangalore jane ka next year and phir se koi trip ka plan banate hai covid ke bad. 
Happy pride month ğŸŒˆğŸŒˆğŸŒˆ

text:
Yo internet playboy, meme lord. Kya hi bakchod hai jab kisi bhi ek chiz me lag jata to gazab hi chapta hai. Esc me A* , vietnam internship, game development and many other achievements jo tu bataya bhi nhi hoga kisi ko sayad. I still remember pubg mere hi mobile par khela tha tu pehli bar uske bad usme bhi pro ban gya. Abhi valo khel rha I am 100% sure usme bhi Immortal/radiant ho jaega tu. 
First year me kya hi bakchodi ki hai humne umang ke sath milkar. kya hi bulla kat te the hum sab bhai mere ya ashu ke room par. First year me tujhe height se dar lagta tha, I still remember kaise piche hokar dekhta tha tu niche. Winter me resident evil khelte time jo teri fatti thi wo to kabhi nhi bhul skta. Lucknow me bhot maje kiye humne tera hi tshirt pehna tha maine ğŸ˜‚. Goa aata to I cannot even imagine kya hi bakchodi hoti. Tere dry pumps wing me kafi logo ko humesha yad rhenge ğŸ˜ğŸ˜. 
Bhai logo ki bhi bakchod party karenge hum sab tu bas aaja bangalore jaldi.

Aur bhai CSE ke chappu boi and wing ke sabse bakchod launde! Apan dono ka sab jgah almost sath me attendance rhta tha. Chahe wo first year ke lectures ho, ncc (altough u were in other group but attendance and frooti ke liye kya hi bhasad mach ti thi), summer me swimming and countless other involvements. First year me shobhit ke sath milkar humne bhot bakchodi ki hai. I cannot even recall all the games we have played together. Yaad hai jab overwatch free hua tha exam ke time ek week ke liye and fir  sudhanshu ke sath milkar resident evil khele the hum sari lights off kar ke. Tera wo first year wala epic GPL to puri wing ko humesha yaad rhega. And thanks to u I met several other amazing people (Aryan, tanmay). You were always there to support me during internship, placements and many other challenging times. Jab bhi koi code me error aata u were my go to person. CPI almost perfect hai, mobile, pc gaming sab me pro hai and bulla bhi itna kat ta tha, koi itna bakchod kaise ho skta hai. I don't know why you never joined music club (though I remember u did give auditions for freshers night). You have an amazing voice. Goa trip was one hell of an experience.
